《'''不会分离'''》是[[光良|光良]]的第五张个人专辑，发行于2007年11月9日。<ref>{{cite news | title= 王光良 - 不會分離 / Michael Wong (Guang Liang) - Never Apart Review | accessdate= 2008-09-18 | url= http://aznplay.com/2007/11/17/album-review-michael-wong-never-apart/ | deadurl= yes | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20081209095844/http://aznplay.com/2007/11/17/album-review-michael-wong-never-apart/ | archivedate= 2008-12-09 }}</ref>专辑包含一张CD和一张DVD。CD是新歌集合（除了第7首，之前以可下载在线单曲的形式发行了）。<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |coauthors= |title=光良最新单曲：I AM WHO I AM我就是我 (12/12在线上架) |date= |publisher= |url=http://www.michael4u.com/_cn/_infomation/show.php?id=79 |work= |pages= |accessdate=2007-11-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071208230505/http://www.michael4u.com/_cn/_infomation/show.php?id=79 |archivedate=2007-12-08 }}</ref>DVD包含了CD第2首歌的MV以及花絮。

